---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Works">

<style>
  .container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 80px auto;
    padding: 0 20px;
    color: #ddd;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .year {
    margin-bottom: 40px;
  }

  .year-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .works {
    line-height: 2;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .container {
      margin: 40px auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 22px;
    }

    .works {
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="container">

  <h1>WORKS</h1>

  <div class="works">

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2025</div>
      »I am all ears« for Orchestra (ca. 7 min.)<br>
      »When the Wind Blows Softly and the Waves are Still« for String Quartet (ca. 7 min.)<br>
      »Hidpulse« for Two Pianos (ca. 8 min.)<br>
      5명의 연주자를 위한 »밝은심연« (ca. 8 min.)<br>
      »Yeon« for Piano Solo<br>
      합창을 위한 »님의 노래« (ca. 5 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2024</div>
      첼로 솔로를 위한 »휘파람 불듯이«<br>
      »Ecto« for Violin solo<br>
      피아노 오중주를 위한 »흩어지다 모이다« (ca. 6 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2023</div>
      »Earnendel« for 7 Players (ca. 8 min.)<br>
      »Rauschen ver. II« for Flute, Piano and Cello (ca. 7 min.)<br>
      »Woher und wohin II« for Violin and Piano (ca. 7 min.)<br>
      바리톤, 첼로, 피아노를 위한 »시김« (ca. 9 min.)<br>
      바이올린, 알토 플루트, 베이스 클라리넷, 타악기를 위한 »나는 떡을 썰테니 너를 글을 쓰거라« (ca. 20 min.)<br>
      »Kollektiver Monolog« for Orchestra (ca. 11 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2022</div>
      »Melos« for Flute, Clarinet in Bb, Piano, Violin and Cello (ca. 12 min.)<br>
      해금과 오르간을 위한 »돌고돌아 강강술래« (ca. 7 min.)<br>
      »Nicht nichts Besonderes« for Clarinet in B, Percussion, Piano and Cello (ca. 9 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2021</div>
      »MacGuffin effect« for Piano solo (ca. 10 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2020</div>
      »Dodecagonal design« for String Quartet (ca. 9 min.)<br>
      »Verzerrung im Spiegel« for Percussion, Accordion and Piano (ca. 9 min.)<br>
      »Rubato« for Flute solo (ca. 7 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2019</div>
      »I see your melody« for Clarinet, Percussion, Harp, Piano and Cello (ca. 9 min.)<br>
      »Distorsion« for Orchestra (ca. 12 min.)<br>
      »Niemand behaupte« for Soprano and Ensemble (ca. 13 min.)<br>
      »Woher und wohin« for Violin solo (ca. 7 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2018</div>
      »Zwei oder eins« for Two Cellos (ca. 12 min.)<br>
      »Scattering« for String Quartet<br>
      »Rauschen« for Oboe, Piano and Cello (ca. 8 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2017</div>
      »Niemand ist da« for Two Percussionists (ca. 9 min.)<br>
      »Dichte« for String Quartet (ca. 15 min.)<br>
      »Fünf kleine Stücke (Stützen)« for Piano solo (ca. 8 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2016</div>
      »Hap« for Orchestra (ca. 12 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2015</div>
      »Die Traumdeutung« for Violin and Piano (ca. 9 min.)<br>
      »Unum De Variatione« for Flute, Cello and Piano (ca. 11 min.)<br>
      »KangKangsulle« for Clarinet in Bb and String Quartet (ca. 10 min.)<br>
      소프라노와 오케스트라를 위한 »마중« (ca. 5 min.)<br>
      소프라노와 피아노를 위한 »마중« (ca. 5 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2014</div>
      »Kyrie« for 8 Voices (ca. 20 min.)<br>
      »Taste for the Arts« for Violin solo (ca. 9 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2013</div>
      »Karman Rhapsody« for Violin and Piano (ca. 11 min.)<br>
      »Meditation for Picasso’s Massacre en Coree« for Flute, Viola and Double Bass (ca. 9 min.)<br>
      »Pumpkin Time« for Piano solo (ca. 9 min.)
    </div>

    <div class="year">
      <div class="year-title">2011</div>
      »Number« for String Quartet (ca. 14 min.)<br>
      4성부합창을 위한 »우리 모두 하나되자« (ca. 3 min.)
    </div>

  </div>

</div>

</Layout>
